# Build and Dependencies

## Targets

- `drone_mapper_simulation`
- `drone_mapper_simulation_test`
- `maps_comparison`

## Build

```bash
cmake --preset default
cmake --build --preset default
```

## Dependencies

Declare in `vcpkg.json` (mp-units, yaml-cpp, cnpy or equivalent, gtest). No manual install in README (e11).

## README

Build/run instructions must match actual CMake presets and binary names.
